body: - - - - About: ============================ MrTheSoulz Profiles For ProbablyEngine. This file lists all the rotation specific stuff bellow. My profile requires the latest Version of PE from GITHUB Download link: https://github.com/ProbablyEngine/Probably If you encounter any issues, report them at the forums, or drop me an email: Email: mrthesoulz@gmail.com Forum: http://goo.gl/QEp17b If you like what i do, dont forget to +rep me. Or if you can buy me a drink Donate Link: http://goo.gl/yrctPO --------------------------------------------------------------- How to install & use: ============================ * Extract the file. * Remove -master from folder name. * Load World of Warcraft. * Right-click PE addon and choose the rotation.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
